Chatbot and AI Voice Assistant
This project involves the creation of a Chatbot and AI Voice Assistant using Python and various machine learning techniques. The bot is capable of responding to user queries in natural language and can also process voice inputs, providing a more interactive experience.

Features
Text-Based Chatbot: Responds to user text queries with intelligent, context-aware responses.
Voice Assistant: Allows users to interact with the assistant via voice commands.
Speech Recognition: Converts spoken language into text for processing.
Text-to-Speech: Converts text responses from the assistant into audible speech.
Technologies Used
Python
Natural Language Processing (NLP)
NLTK, SpaCy
Speech Recognition
Google Speech API
Text-to-Speech (TTS)
pyttsx3
OpenAI GPT-3 or any alternative AI model
Flask (for web integration)
